Package robot

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BDemo
    The behavior class for the demo mode
    BIdle
    The behavior class for when the robot is doing nothing.
    BKill
    The behavior class for the used to kill the program when escape is pressed
    BottomMotor
    The motor class for the bottom motor of the robot.
    BUser
    Behavior class for the user mode e.g when the robot is controlled using a game controller
    ColorSensor
    The class for the color sensor, which is used to determine where objects are sorted
    ControllerTest
    Just a test class for the controller, not used in the actual runnable project
    Main
    The main class which is run on the robot Behavior's priority is determined by it's position in behaviorArray.
    MiddleMotor
    The motor class for the middle motor of the robot.
    MotorTest
    Just a test class for testing the boundaries of the robot's movements.
    Navigator
    A high level class which contains methods to rotate all motors to a specific place on the working surface
    TireDemo
    Just a demo of the robot lifting a tire and then dropping it.
    TopMotor
    The motor class for the top most motor of the robot, the "hand" part.
    TouchSensor
    Class for the touch sensor used to stop BottomMotor before it hits anything
    TwoTiresTwoCups
    A high level class that determines the movements of all motors during the demo mode
    User
    The class for the user mode of the robot
